This folder contains all the grammar files that are used to generate sentences with different gramatical constructs.

# EXECUTING "generate":
The sentence generator has been written in Python.
The "generate" file can be executed on UNIX Platforms using the command
./generate <grammar_file> <no. of sentences>

If you're using any other platform, or there are any problems running the program,
the original python file "generate.py" is also provided, which can be run
like so:
python generate.py grammmar1 10
